    "content": "Here\u0026#39;s a tip for soldering LED strips:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFirst prime the strips by tinning each pad. Hold your iron against the pad for 5-10 seconds so it heats up, then melt some solder to the pad. If it isn\u0026#39;t sticking well, you need more heat.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAfter the strips are primed like this, solder your wires on.",
