    "content": "Thanks for all the suggestions, guys!  I also found these, which look very helpful (but a bit bulky): \u003ca rel\u003d\"nofollow\" target\u003d\"_blank\" href\u003d\"https://blinkinlabs.myshopify.com/collections/frontpage/products/led-strip-repair-kit-for-apn102-dotstar-strips-10-pieces\" class\u003d\"ot-anchor bidi_isolate\" jslog\u003d\"10929; track:click\" dir\u003d\"ltr\"\u003ehttps://blinkinlabs.myshopify.com/collections/frontpage/products/led-strip-repair-kit-for-apn102-dotstar-strips-10-pieces\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eStefan, that looks great!  I definitely have to try that now.  :) Not sure how I missed that video.  How many LEDs are in that lamp?",
